---
interface Props {
  bgColor?: string;
}

const { bgColor = 'bg-slate-100' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class={`px-6 py-16 md:py-24 ${bgColor}`}>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
        Roof Questions? We Answer Them.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        These are the questions we hear every week from Arizona homeowners.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Do you work with all Arizona insurance companies?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Yes. We've worked with every major insurance company in Arizona—State Farm, Allstate, Farmers, USAA, Liberty Mutual, and dozens more. We know how each company operates and what documentation they require.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>How long does the roof inspection take?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Typically 30-45 minutes. We'll inspect your entire roof, document any damage with photos, check your attic for interior issues, and walk you through everything we find. You'll leave with a clear understanding of your roof's condition.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What if my insurance denies my claim?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          We help with appeals. Insurance companies sometimes deny legitimate claims, but we know how to document damage properly and advocate for you. If your claim is denied, we'll review the decision and help you understand your options for appeal.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Is there really no obligation?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Absolutely zero obligation. We'll inspect your roof, tell you what we find, and explain your options. Whether you move forward with us, choose another contractor, or decide to wait—that's completely up to you. No pressure. No sales tactics.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Do you handle the insurance paperwork?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Yes. We handle everything: filing the claim, meeting with your adjuster, providing documentation, and negotiating the scope of work. You'll never have to call your insurance company or deal with confusing paperwork.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>How soon can you schedule an inspection?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Usually within 24-48 hours. We serve the entire Phoenix metro area and can often accommodate same-day or next-day inspections depending on your schedule and our availability.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What areas of Arizona do you serve?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          We serve Mesa, Tempe, Scottsdale, Gilbert, Chandler, Phoenix, Apache Junction, Queen Creek, Fountain Hills, Paradise Valley, Glendale, Peoria, and surrounding areas within 25 miles of Mesa.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 8 -->
      <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition shadow-md">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Will the inspection damage my roof further?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#76ba41] group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          No. Our inspectors are trained to walk roofs safely without causing damage. We use proper techniques and take precautions to protect your roof during the inspection. We've inspected thousands of roofs across Arizona without incident.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <!-- Still Have Questions CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a 
        href="#form"
        class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-[#76ba41] text-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[#5fa033] transition duration-200"
      >
        Still have questions? Let’s talk.
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>